{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 68,
    "name": "سُورَةُ القَلَمِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Qalam",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Pen",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 52,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5272,
        "text": "Nun. By the Pen and what they write:",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5273,
        "text": "by your Lord’s blessing, you are not, crazy,",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5274,
        "text": "and yours indeed will be an everlasting reward,",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5275,
        "text": "and indeed you possess a great character.",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5276,
        "text": "You will see and they will see,",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5277,
        "text": "which one of you is crazy.",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5278,
        "text": "Indeed your Lord knows best those who stray from His way, and He knows best those who are guided.",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5279,
        "text": "So do not obey the deniers,",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5280,
        "text": "who are eager that you should be flexible, so that they [too] may be flexible [towards you].",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5281,
        "text": "And do not obey any vile swearer,",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5282,
        "text": "scandal-monger, talebearer,",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5283,
        "text": "hinderer of all good, sinful transgressor,",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5284,
        "text": "callous and, on top of that, baseborn",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5285,
        "text": "—[who behaves in such a manner only] because he has wealth and children.",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5286,
        "text": "When Our signs are recited to him, he says, ‘Myths of the ancients!’",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 564,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5287,
        "text": "Soon We shall brand him on his snout.",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5288,
        "text": "Indeed we have tested them just as We tested the People of the Garden when they vowed they would gather its fruit at dawn,",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5289,
        "text": "and they did not make any exception.",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5290,
        "text": "Then, a visitation from your Lord visited it while they were asleep.",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5291,
        "text": "So, by dawn it was like a harvested field.",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5292,
        "text": "At dawn they called out to one another,",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5293,
        "text": "‘Get off early to your field if you have to gather [the fruits].’",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5294,
        "text": "So off they went, murmuring to one another:",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5295,
        "text": "‘Today no needy man shall come to you in it.’",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5296,
        "text": "And they set out at early morning, [considering themselves] able to deprive [the poor of its fruit].",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5297,
        "text": "But when they saw it, they said, ‘We have indeed lost our way!’",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5298,
        "text": "‘No, it is we who have been deprived!’",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5299,
        "text": "The most upright among them said, ‘Did I not tell you, ‘‘Why do you not glorify [Allah]?’’ ’",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5300,
        "text": "They said, ‘Immaculate is our Lord! We have indeed been wrongdoers!’",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5301,
        "text": "Then they turned to one another, blaming each other.",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5302,
        "text": "They said, ‘Woe to us! Indeed, we have been rebellious.",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5303,
        "text": "Maybe our Lord will give us a better one in its place. Indeed we earnestly beseech our Lord.’",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5304,
        "text": "Such was their punishment; and the punishment of the Hereafter is surely greater, had they known.",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 498,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5305,
        "text": "Indeed for the Godwary there will be gardens of bliss near their Lord.",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5306,
        "text": "Shall We treat those who submit [to Us] as [We treat] the guilty?",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5307,
        "text": "What is the matter with you? How do you judge!",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5308,
        "text": "Do you possess a scripture in which you read",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5309,
        "text": "that you shall have in it whatever you choose?",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5310,
        "text": "Do you have a pledge binding on Us until the Day of Resurrection, that you shall indeed have whatever you decide?",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5311,
        "text": "Ask them, which of them will aver [any of] that!",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5312,
        "text": "Do they have any ‘partners’ [that they claim for Allah]? Then let them produce their partners, if they are truthful.",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5313,
        "text": "The day when the catastrophe occurs and they are summoned to prostrate themselves, they will not be able [to do it].",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 565,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5314,
        "text": "With a humbled look [in their eyes], they will be overcast by abasement. Certainly, they were summoned to prostrate themselves while they were yet sound.",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5315,
        "text": "So leave Me with those who deny this discourse. We will draw them imperceptibly [into ruin], whence they do not know.",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5316,
        "text": "I will grant them respite, for My devising is indeed sure.",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5317,
        "text": "Do you ask them for a reward, so that they are weighed down with debt?",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5318,
        "text": "Do they possess [access to] the Unseen, so that they write it down?",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5319,
        "text": "So submit patiently to the judgement of your Lord, and do not be like the Man of the Fish who called out as he choked with grief.",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5320,
        "text": "Had it not been for a blessing that came to his rescue from his Lord, he would surely have been cast on the bare shore, being blameworthy.",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5321,
        "text": "So his Lord chose him and made him one of the righteous.",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5322,
        "text": "Indeed the faithless almost devour you with their eyes when they hear this Reminder, and they say, ‘He is indeed crazy.’",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5323,
        "text": "Yet it is just a reminder for all the nations.",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 566,
        "ruku": 499,
        "hizbQuarter": 226,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
